{"type": "article", "id": 31864, "title": "玛莎百货大幅裁员，以及，Dior 绿色唇膏不知道是什么效果 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-06T02:28:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 32468, "name": "Dior 唇膏"}, {"id": 32469, "name": "Dad Hat"}, {"id": 32470, "name": "欧洲时尚电商"}, {"id": 321, "name": "Amazon"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 2897, "name": "玛莎百货"}, {"id": 9220, "name": "日本乐天"}, {"id": 15116, "name": "Y-3"}, {"id": 21494, "name": "Côte & Ciel"}, {"id": 32471, "name": "N.HOOLYWOOD"}, {"id": 32472, "name": "Reebok Classic"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160906092439Q1Jj3ZgSe76bGYXO.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/mergers-acquisitions/rakuten-buys-c2c-fashion-marketplace-app-fril-10520874/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>日本乐天集团收购时尚平台 app Fril</b></a> | 日本乐天集团全资买下了 Fril 的母公司 Fablic。Fril 成立于 2012 年，是日本首个 C2C 模式的电子交易平台，其 app 下载量突破 500 万。不过，乐天集团并未透露这笔交易的具体金额。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/mass-off-price/british-retailer-marks-spencer-to-cut-525-positions-steve-rowe-10520914/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>英国最大的零售集团玛莎百货要大幅度裁员</b></a> | 为了重组并提高效率，玛莎百货昨日宣布英国总部要裁员 525 人，这占据了它伦敦办公室的 15% 的员工数量。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/amazon-spurs-e-commerce-acquisitions-consolidation-galeries-lafayette-bazarchic-vente-privee-designers-and-friends-10521236/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Amazon 加速了欧洲时尚电商的市场竞争</b></a> | 由于 Amazon 也加入了欧洲时尚电商的竞争中，其他的欧洲零售商之间的并购加速了。昨日，法国零售集团 Galeries Lafayette Group 宣布收购电商 BazarChic 。法国闪购电商领导者 Vente-Privée 宣布收购丹麦电商 Designers &amp; Friends 。伦敦咨询公司 ResearchFarm 的研究员 Daniel Lucht 称，Amazon 助推了欧洲零售商之间并购的白热化。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/hm-collaborates-london-college-of-fashion-sustainability-project-10521026/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>H&amp;M 与伦敦时装学院展开合作</b></a> | 为了更好地把握流行，H&amp;M 与伦敦时装学院开始了一个长期合作的项目。在伦敦时装学院 BA 时尚珠宝以及 BA 时尚设计与技术课程上，学生将被分为 33 个小组，为 H&amp;M 的女装系列贡献灵感。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">法国品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/cote-ciel-2016\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Côte &amp; Ciel</a> 一直以设计感和高质量著称（虽然有些已经成了街款），近日，它发布了它的秋冬新品系列，在经典型款上继续改良，特别使用了不同的材质，展现不同的质感。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906094416QVm6KFSJAztBqvsf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906094416doMJvAulbNFQj9PI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906094416y8ouC3kLtDnGIK2R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906094416NJPQeW46FzypE5Ok.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906094425sUBOEMtiCpLQf68X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906094427qCO6flDTBogtXmwK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666835\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906094428lacAq0pr9KxwnkCI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906094434TpyNI9clskDY1jOM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Dior 推出 Rouge Dior 系列唇膏新品。有黄色、粉橙、紫色、绿色等多种颜色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906094019udg1VjBkXz6nJKAv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">拉斯维加斯街头名店 Feature Sneaker Boutique 推出<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/y-3-2016-fall-winter-editorial-by-feature\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Y-3 系列造型穿搭特辑</a>。Y-3 2016 秋冬系列新品已经登陆 Feature 官方网店，售价为 90 至 420 美元。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093936psxioB63SHP2lzRA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093958CWlgjFdTMRiXowVy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609060940103tlSunsJFBD6YINb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>作为 2016 最具人气的配饰设计之一，A Bathing Ape 于今年秋冬也推出多款不同色彩的<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/a-bathing-ape-2016-dad-hats\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Dad Hat </a>帽款。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093857Ovl5Dcpij69raLuR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093857w3Sgk685E9xdlQvz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093858X3lVpSR0giMOmbz2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093857rxuC36IYQRhTU7Fp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016090609390881GlUXxpgzAnTskC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093908WYFKyZNH4pI1qr7B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/puma-x-ueg-2016-fw-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Puma 与波兰街头品牌 UEG 合作，推出一系列秋冬联名单品</a>。该系列名为 Gravity Resistance ，主题是以宇宙为灵感的科幻美学，并融入了 UEG 所主打的可循环环保理念和极简实验风格。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093812OKnHvIoU2F4bSYcM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093812el8syjvz4nCNxJ9V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093812H2AIRKLwVXTUYJoG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093818ixQqM2ja7G8R4TOw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093823HxKtIbOzlYRS1p6c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>日本时尚品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/n-hoolywood-x-reebok-classic-2016\" rel=\"nofollow\">N.HOOLYWOOD 与 Reebok Classic 推出全新的联名系列</a>。这个系列包括 9 件单品，运用了高档针织结合运动机能材质打造。定价从 14990 到 45990 日元不等。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093610GYPheQqBlmJ7aTIy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093610ZIcU8MBEqpwdkAJY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093610k7zRx0rAsmoFCLSY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093617dAhX1tcFGfUqY9bH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609060936170jhuOYFnfvaoNA7k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093624zTO30MeP5jVK9FWy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093624uphi29n5AebzkOFa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906093624soiWpbVYcQqdECJv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}